{"tid":1316024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「FACT CHECK」都無證，你又知佢係警察？","createTime":"2019-07-14T15:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T15:31:11.000Z","uid":32906,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0ca4d62ff7f2c9b47a73ef2fa39faafd0a670ff0","tid":1316024,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">現場冇人肯定佢係警察</span></span><br />\n網上大家都以為佢係警察<br />\n但我認為佢只係一個冒充警察嘅不知名人士<br />\n佢穿上類似警察嘅裝備追打示威者<br />\n<br />\n最後被圍<br />\n<br />\n佢地無襲過警！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xKhnZm4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxKhnZm4.png&h=8530b580&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明顯無證 盾上無警察二字<br />\n邊個知呀"},{"pid":"f830c6ce780d57e59acf9293bc4c63967023d729","tid":1316024,"uid":176166,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:19:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1caa377aea8b2445638292de10af9f9905b11b55","tid":1316024,"uid":32906,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:22:16.000Z","msg":"如果最後佢，記招公開出示番委任證<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁sorry囉</span>"},{"pid":"b9735ff406d582dde002683985ced06b9348c84a","tid":1316024,"uid":230703,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:23:49.000Z","msg":"我點知佢係警察，又無號碼，又無pass,  我估佢可能係示威者扮警察。"},{"pid":"f95a6933002f57d1c7d610d81e72ee009d9ed532","tid":1316024,"uid":59700,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:24:50.000Z","msg":"冒警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ebcd4bc74cb50a428d3186eb6f5